# AI Sentiment Analyzer

## Project Overview

The AI Sentiment Analyzer is a Python-based application that uses Natural Language Processing (NLP) to analyze the sentiment of user-provided text. It determines whether the sentiment is Positive, Negative, or Neutral by calculating the polarity score using the TextBlob library.

