## Project Scope

This project is designed to:
- Analyze user text sentiment.
- Classify text as Positive, Negative, or Neutral.
- Demonstrate the basics of Natural Language Processing (NLP).
- Serve as a beginner-friendly AI and Python project.
- Help understand sentiment analysis techniques used in real-world applications.

